04:14.296 --> 04:18.045
“The truth is rarely
pure and never simple.”

04:18.433 --> 04:19.966
Oscar Wilde.

04:19.968 --> 04:21.935
See that shadow
on the wall?

04:21.937 --> 04:24.170
It shifted
as the sun went down,

04:24.172 --> 04:26.039
but now it's back.

04:26.041 --> 04:28.608
The video was on
a 6-hour loop before it repeated,

04:28.610 --> 04:30.476
which is why no one
noticed it right away.

04:30.478 --> 04:33.279
So this was organized
and premeditated.

04:33.281 --> 04:35.081
Ok, so even though
this isn't the real footage,

04:35.083 --> 04:37.483
the lobby would have been
crowded with tourists at the time.

04:37.485 --> 04:39.886
How was she taken in broad daylight
from a public place?

04:39.888 --> 04:42.155
Ironically, it may have been
easier to kidnap her in a crowd.

04:42.157 --> 04:44.824
It's noisy, hard to see,
people are distracted.

04:44.826 --> 04:46.125
If she was injected
with a sedative,

04:46.127 --> 04:47.827
the kidnappers might
just look like friends or family

04:47.829 --> 04:49.429
helping someone
who was feeling ill.

04:49.431 --> 04:51.531
We'll set up a trace phone,
and I've already got agents

04:51.533 --> 04:53.733
looking into terrorism and
organized crime connections.

04:53.735 --> 04:55.735
I also need to know
on what committees you sit

04:55.737 --> 04:58.204
and what pending bills might
be influenced by your vote.

04:58.206 --> 05:00.073
Right. I'm on the energy
subcommittee.

05:00.075 --> 05:02.809
There's a vote in two days
to ban fracking on the Pacific Coast.

05:02.811 --> 05:04.611
Where do you stand
on the issue?

05:04.613 --> 05:06.779
I'm for the ban, but
I've been getting pressure

05:06.781 --> 05:08.348
from the oil companies
to vote against it.

05:08.350 --> 05:09.949
They're not the most
subtle people in the world.

05:09.951 --> 05:11.451
Do you think maybe they have
something to do with this?

05:11.453 --> 05:13.720
Well, just to be safe,
I think you and your family

05:13.722 --> 05:15.355
should stay here
in protective custody

05:15.357 --> 05:16.856
until we get a better
handle on things.

05:16.858 --> 05:18.658
Ok. It's just my brother
and my mother.

05:18.660 --> 05:19.826
They're in Georgetown.

05:19.828 --> 05:21.160
They live together?

05:21.162 --> 05:22.795
Paul just got out of rehab
a couple of months ago.

05:22.797 --> 05:24.664
He's staying with her till
he gets back on his feet.

05:24.666 --> 05:26.165
We'll arrange to have them picked up.
Agent Anderson,

05:26.167 --> 05:28.201
will you please show the Congressman
where he can stay?

05:28.203 --> 05:31.404
Sure. Congressman,
right this way.

05:32.641 --> 05:34.641
So, uh, we confirmed
the Congressman

05:34.643 --> 05:36.309
was in his office
all afternoon.

05:36.311 --> 05:38.177
There was nothing unusual
about his behavior.

05:38.179 --> 05:40.647
And he's responding
appropriately.

05:40.649 --> 05:43.850
Yeah, Dave,
what have you got?

05:43.852 --> 05:45.385
We'll be right down.

05:45.387 --> 05:48.621
Organized crime may have
a lead on the case.

05:48.623 --> 05:49.989
So who's the package?

05:49.991 --> 05:53.126
Who cares? Dyadya just said
it's someone important.

05:53.128 --> 05:54.527
What's our piece
of the action?

05:54.529 --> 05:55.962
Maybe 5 grand.

05:58.767 --> 06:01.734
Which translates into,
“he'll call us, we just sit tight.”

06:01.736 --> 06:03.102
These are low-level guys?

06:03.104 --> 06:04.871
Foot soldiers in
the the Mikhalov Bratva,

06:04.873 --> 06:07.473
a Russian crime ring
that deals in illegal arms.

06:07.475 --> 06:10.777
We intercepted a container
of Stinger missiles about 6 months ago

06:10.779 --> 06:12.378
they were gonna ship
to Syria.

06:12.380 --> 06:14.113
Been trying to infiltrate
the ring since then,

06:14.115 --> 06:15.948
figure out who
the major players are.

06:15.950 --> 06:17.450
Where is the wiretap?

06:17.452 --> 06:19.752
In their apartment.
This recording is from a week ago.

06:19.754 --> 06:22.288
And you think it's connected
to Sophie Troy?

06:22.290 --> 06:23.756
Well, here's what we know.

06:23.758 --> 06:26.793
These low-level guys often do
freelance work to pad their income.

06:26.795 --> 06:29.562
You need somebody for an unsavory job,
this is who you call.

06:29.564 --> 06:31.397
1-800-thug.

06:31.399 --> 06:32.965
Yeah, pretty much.
This kidnapping

06:32.967 --> 06:35.068
they're talking about
was gonna go down around now.

06:35.070 --> 06:36.436
Well, probably
not a coincidence.

06:36.438 --> 06:38.838
According to Loker,
our agent on site,

06:38.840 --> 06:41.841
they're still waiting for Dyadya,
which means uncle, to call.

06:41.843 --> 06:43.276
Any idea who uncle is?

06:43.278 --> 06:45.645
No. We've been trying
to I.D. him, but no luck so far.

06:45.647 --> 06:47.714
I think we need
to be on this.

06:47.716 --> 06:50.616
You're welcome to join us as long
as you don't jeopardize our case.

06:50.618 --> 06:53.019
Understood.

